[thinking] I'm thinking about whether I need to make this interface public. There’s the option of having a nested public interface, but I need to weigh the pros and cons of visibility. I should consider what kind of accessibility is required and if making it public adds value to its usability. It’s like deciding if sharing a tool with everyone is worth it — will it lead to better outcomes or just more confusion?
